    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-6">
      <a href="#contact" class="bg-amber-400 text-brand px-8 py-4 font-bold text-lg rounded-md hover:bg-amber-300 transition-colors">
        Bestil rapport — 2.495 kr
      </a>
      <a href="#demo" class="border border-white/20 text-white/80 px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-lg rounded-md hover:border-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors">
